high_descs: Walk ahead a few steps and then left towards the bread on the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread.
Turn around and veer left to the fridge.
Place the bread in the fridge, to the right of the apple.  Close the door, wait a moment, and then take the bread out again.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter.
Place the bread on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on a counter.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the loaf of bread off of the counter.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the loaf of bread inside to the right of the apple, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge remove the loaf of bread and close the door.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, turn left to face the counter once past the sink.
Put the chilled loaf of bread on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled loaf of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter with the loaf of bread.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the counter.
Turn and take the bread to the fridge.
Cool the loaf of bread in the fridge.
Take the cooled bread to the counter by the toaster.
Set the cooled bread down on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Set a cold loaf of bread on the counter in front of the toaster.
